                  i.bi.bi-check-circle.me-2
                  | Prerequisites
              .card-body
                p.mb-3 Before we begin, make sure you have:
                ul.mb-0
                  li An Azure account (create a free one at
                    a(href='https://azure.microsoft.com', target='_blank', rel='noopener') azure.microsoft.com
                    | )
                  li A GitHub account
                  li Basic knowledge of Git

