              .card-header.bg-success.text-white
                h3.h5.mb-0
                  i.bi.bi-2-circle.me-2
                  | Step 2: Create the Azure Static Web App
              .card-body
                .accordion#step2-accordion
                  .accordion-item
                    h4.accordion-header#headingSignIn
                      button.accordion-button(
                        type='button'
                        data-bs-toggle='collapse'
                        data-bs-target='#collapseSignIn'
